text: Ic seah on bearwe beam hlifian, tanum torhtne.
Þæt treow wæs on wynne, wudu weaxende.
Wæter hine ond eorþe feddan fægre, oþþæt he frod dagum on oþrum wearð aglachade deope gedolgod, dumb in bendum, wriþen ofer wunda, wonnum hyrstum foran gefrætwed.
Nu he fæcnum <weg> þurh his heafdes <mægen> hildegieste oþrum rymeð.
Oft hy an <yste> strudon hord ætgædre; hræd wæs ond unlæt se æftera, gif se ærra fær genamnan in nearowe neþan moste.
